Paul Scholes has criticised Mario Mandzukic for over reacting after the Atletico Madrid striker appeared to be punched and bitten by Real Madrid 's Daniel Carvajal .
Croatian striker was in on-pitch scraps with Sergio Ramos , Raphael Varane and Carvalajal during the Champions League quarter-final first leg at the Vicente Calderon .
Scholes says Atletico star was over-reacting to the challenges made on him .